headline: Qualcomm Announces Dr. Baaziz Achour Appointed Chief Technology Officer-Elect
summary: SAN DIEGO, December 12, 2024--Qualcomm Incorporated (NASDAQ: QCOM) today announced the appointment of Dr. Baaziz Achour to the role of Chief Technology Officer, Qualcomm Technologies, Inc., and the retirement of Dr. James Thompson, each effective February 3, 2025. Dr. Achour currently serves as Deputy Chief Technology Officer.
